== Overview ==
The Photonic Sphere uses a 360 degree projection giving it a much higher defense rating. However its weight and power usage can be a drain.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Photonic Sphere can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
